# MARKETING & CONTENT SERVICES

## 1. AI Content Creation

**Description:**
Automated generation of high-quality written content for blogs, websites, emails, and social media. AI analyzes your brand voice and creates consistent, engaging content at scale.

**What's Included:**
- Blog posts (500-2000 words)
- Social media captions & posts
- Email newsletters
- Product descriptions
- Website copy
- Editing & proofreading

**Pricing:**
- Blog post: $50-150/post
- Social media posts: $15-30/post
- Email sequences (5 emails): $100-250
- Monthly content retainer: $500-2000/month

---

## 2. Professional Copywriting

